paragraphs.text:
%MicrosoftSQL
select 
count(1) AS Claims_Count, sum(CLCL.CLCL_TOT_CHG) AS Total_Charge, sum(CLCL.CLCL_TOT_PAYABLE) AS Total_Payable,
CLCL.CLCL_CUR_STS, CLCL.CLCL_INPUT_DT, CLCL.CSCS_ID, CLCL.CSPI_ID, CLCL.PDPD_ID, CLCL.NWPR_PFX, CLCL.NWNW_ID,GRGR.GRGR_ID
from fabncpr0..CMC_CLCL_CLAIM  CLCL, 
fabncpr0..CMC_GRGR_GROUP GRGR
WHERE 
CLCL.CLCL_CUR_STS IN (01,02) AND
CLCL.CSPD_CAT IN ('M') AND 
CLCL.CLCL_INPUT_DT > ${Start_Date='07-01-2017'}AND
CLCL.CLCL_INPUT_DT < ${End_Date='07-01-2018'}AND
GRGR.GRGR_CK = CLCL.GRGR_CK 
GROUP BY
CLCL.CLCL_CUR_STS, CLCL.CLCL_INPUT_DT, CLCL.CSCS_ID, CLCL.CSPI_ID, CLCL.PDPD_ID, CLCL.NWPR_PFX, CLCL.NWNW_ID,GRGR.GRGR_ID--, CLCL_TOT_CHG, CLCL_TOT_PAYABLE
ORDER BY
CLCL_INPUT_DT
